Package: mcdaHub
Title: Unified Multi-Criteria Decision Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Wanting", "Zuo", , "ttlucky625@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for Multi-Criteria Decision Analysis (MCDA)
    using R6 classes for object-oriented design. Provides multiple MCDA methods
    (TOPSIS, PROMETHEE, AHP) for ranking, sorting, and choice problems. Includes
    sensitivity analysis tools and toy datasets for examples.
